<view class="page-shell glossary-page">
  <view class="glossary-hero page-pad">
    <view class="eyebrow">概念谱系</view>
    <view class="display-title">不是词典，<br />而是概念的迁徙史</view>
    <view class="rule"></view>
    <view class="hero-copy">同一个词会穿越不同思想制度：Logos 从宇宙法则成为“道”，Arche 从自然本原成为创世权能，共相之争则一路通向现代个体主义。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="search-wrap page-pad">
    <view class="search-box">
      <text class="search-icon">⌕</text>
      <input
        class="search-input"
        value="{{keyword}}"
        placeholder="搜索中文、原文或核心问题"
        placeholder-class="search-placeholder"
        bindinput="onInput"
      />
      <button class="clear-button" wx:if="{{keyword}}" bindtap="clearSearch">清除</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <scroll-view class="category-scroll" scroll-x enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}">
    <view class="category-row">
      <button
        wx:for="{{categories}}"
        wx:key="*this"
        class="category {{activeCategory == item ? 'category-active' : ''}}"
        data-category="{{item}}"
        bindtap="selectCategory"
      >{{item}}</button>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>

  <view class="result-bar page-pad">
    <text>{{resultCount}} 个概念</text>
    <text class="result-category">{{activeCategory}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="term-list page-pad" wx:if="{{resultCount}}">
    <view class="term-card paper-card" wx:for="{{filteredTerms}}" wx:key="term">
      <view class="term-top">
        <view>
          <view class="term-category">{{item.category}}</view>
          <view class="term-name">{{item.term}}</view>
          <view class="term-original">{{item.original}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="term-index">{{index + 1 < 10 ? "0" + (index + 1) : index + 1}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="term-brief">{{item.brief}}</view>
      <view class="term-evolution">
        <view class="evolution-label">概念迁徙</view>
        <view>{{item.evolution}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="term-footer">
        <text class="term-footer-label">相关讲次</text>
        <view class="lecture-links">
          <button
            class="lecture-chip"
            wx:for="{{item.lectureIds}}"
            wx:key="*this"
            wx:for-item="lectureId"
            data-id="{{lectureId}}"
            bindtap="goLecture"
          >第{{lectureId}}讲</button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="empty page-pad" wx:else>
    <view class="empty-mark">∅</view>
    <view class="empty-title">没有找到相关概念</view>
    <view class="empty-copy">试试“秩序”“灵魂”“Logos”或切换分类。</view>
  </view>
</view>
